title: Palram Harmony™ Green Greenhouses - Simple, Clean, Wise
description:
Best-selling greenhouse with smart & clean design:
• Clear as glass, strong as steel
• Lockable door handle
• Magnetic door stopper
• Virtually unbreakable Polycarbonate
• Rust resistant aluminum frame
• Integrated roof Vent kit
• Collect your rainwater using 4 structured gutter heads
• Accessorize your greenhouse
• Twin Shelf Kit
• Heavy Duty Shelf Kit
• Side louver window
• Auto louver opener
• Auto Vent Opener
• Shade Net
• Snow load - 75kg/m2 - 15lbs/ft2
• Harmony greenhouse family - a range of sizes
• 5 years warranty
